Description: Process Exporter with eBPF Network Monitoring
 A high-performance Prometheus exporter for dynamic process monitoring
 with eBPF-based network traffic tracking.
 .
 Features:
  - Dynamic process registration via REST API
  - CPU, memory, disk I/O, and network traffic statistics of processes